In numbers
In the year 2012 more than three million tourists visited from all world Israel.
Most adventurers and to recovery-searching came from Russia, France, Germany, Italy, England, the USA and Ukraine.
Of January until October 2012 came 118.8 a Thousand Ukrainian tourists into the Praised Country, what corresponds to a rise of 51% opposite the comparable time span in the year 2010, before the cancellation of the visa duty on 9th February 2011.
